      Global menu disappears
    - Fix LP: #813775 - Hitting an assertion in dbusmenu
    - Fix LP: #861565 - No buttons in the "Show All Bookmarks" dialog

 -- Chris Coulson <chris.coulson@canonical.com>  Wed, 20 Jun 2012 18:17:11 +0100

