firefox (3.6+nobinonly-0ubuntu5) lucid; urgency=low

  [ Micah Gersten <micahg@ubuntu.com> ]
  * fix LP: #514108 - Cookie Accept Dialog Not Shown on Firefox 3.6; install chrome/comm.* libraries
    - update debian/rules
